{"tid":1029958,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次見，一邊 interview, 一邊食煙","createTime":"2019-02-20T15:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T00:46:25.000Z","uid":162866,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c963321decbaa911769b5caeb633d855d4f74e69","tid":1029958,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"最近，見咗間通訊設備公司，真係大開眼界。<br />\n<br />\n1st In, 就 In HR 個阿Head, 對方係好nice, 不過呢，我坐係房到，等咗成55分鐘先有得In.<br />\n<br />\n好啦，叫做過咗HR嗰關，話即係見老細做2nd In.<br />\n<br />\n點知呢，一坐低，對方就自動點煙了。仲要呢，佢一路食煙，一路向住我塊面噴煙。我真係覺得好唔尊重，心惗，搞錯呀。<br />\n<br />\n而且，我明明見另一個職位，嗰個腦細竟然話，不如考慮下做Sales 先，做得好Sales, 就先轉份去原本見嗰個職位。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我只有禮貌地話，唔好意思，我惗Sales未必適合我呀，多謝你哋今日嘅時間。<br />\n<br />\n走人時，真係覺得，呢個interview真係第一次遇見呢D遭遇，真係浪費咗半日嘅時間。"},{"pid":"bd9806e7cdd31600e05c3d22b6cd3154a246fa86","tid":1029958,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:16:10.000Z","msg":"邊間垃圾，咁唔尊重都有嘅？開名啦"},{"pid":"eb0a7bcbb8100355ff88394df9efb4af35a16cd2","tid":1029958,"uid":46042,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"你咪問佢攞支煙食囉"},{"pid":"ee1af3d52a2ebd05b4dc24a82c825a15a195c5a1","tid":1029958,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:19:36.000Z","msg":"開名"},{"pid":"f4f65f0b8f84ae554e4b14fabac3cbdd4c435cb4","tid":1029958,"uid":171594,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"開名"},{"pid":"71e6ae6911b2376fc7cf3214ebc84455431177f8","tid":1029958,"uid":162866,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T16:02:47.000Z","msg":"廢是開名比人起底"},{"pid":"978952fefbf7b1bdcdbe1fe83d1fade0ed04a316","tid":1029958,"uid":71624,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"71e6ae6911b2376fc7cf3214ebc84455431177f8","tid":1029958,"uid":162866,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T16:02:47.000Z","msg":"廢是開名比人起底"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T17:23:3